safetyInstructions.en: Wear protective clothing. Do not spray during windy conditions. Keep away from water sources.
safetyInstructions.om: Uffata eegumsa uffadhu. Qilleensa cimaa keessatti hin faffacaasin. Madda bishaanii irraa fageeessi.
safetyInstructions.am: መከላከያ ልብስ ይልበሱ። በነፋስ ጊዜ አይርጩ። ከውሃ ምንጮች ያርቁ።

safetyInstructions.en: Use protective equipment. Avoid contact with skin and eyes. Store in cool, dry place.
safetyInstructions.om: Meeshaalee eegumsa fayyadami. Gogaa fi ija waliin wal qunnamtii dhowwi. Iddoo qabbanaawaa fi gogaa keessatti kuusi.
safetyInstructions.am: መከላከያ መሳሪያዎችን ይጠቀሙ። ከቆዳ እና ከዓይን ጋር መገናኘትን ያስወግዱ። በቀዝቃዛ እና ደረቅ ቦታ ያስቀምጡ።

safetyInstructions.en: Highly toxic. Use full protective equipment. Do not eat, drink or smoke during application.
safetyInstructions.om: Summii cimaa qaba. Meeshaalee eegumsa guutuu fayyadami. Yeroo fayyadamtu nyaachuu, dhuguu ykn tamboo hin xuuxin.
safetyInstructions.am: በጣም መርዛማ ነው። ሙሉ መከላከያ መሳሪያ ይጠቀሙ። በመርጨት ጊዜ አይብሉ፣ አይጠጡ ወይም አያጨሱ።
